{"tid":2225565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牧童笛師","createTime":"2020-10-01T12:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T12:31:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a01a6608bdbe04c65fd3390178c82d03254fdcfc","tid":2225565,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"【牧童笛VS大聲公】<br />\n<br />\n港警不准掛標語、不准叫任何口號、不准上街、不准聚集，那用牧童笛公開演奏還可以麼?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/4438960022845148/?vh=e&amp;extid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F454004001340790%2Fposts%2F4438960022845148%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3D0&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1xn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=3a7ad535\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/4438960022845148/?vh=e&amp;extid=0</a>"},{"pid":"64498a71c67bafb71ed76d5c5cbed9cd46a75a80","tid":2225565,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"好似瘋狂ss佢"},{"pid":"459a1f5827c6d29633ca5cfe0828175a5f6c858a","tid":2225565,"uid":67860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"根據 《簡易程序治罪條例》第 4(15) 條：「在公眾街道或道路上奏玩任何樂器；但根據及按照警務處處長運用絕對酌情決定權發出的一般或特別許可證的條件奏玩者，則屬例外」。簡而言之，任何人未在警方牌照科申領《在公眾街道或道路奏玩樂器許可證》的人，即屬違法。"}]}